### 4. Criar Credencial
POST {{baseUrl}}/credentials
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Facebook",
  "url": "https://www.facebook.com",
  "username": "joao.silva",
  "password": "minhasenha123"
}

### 5. Listar todas as Credenciais
GET {{baseUrl}}/credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Buscar Credencial por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/credentials/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Atualizar Credencial
PUT {{baseUrl}}/credentials/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Facebook Atualizado",
  "url": "https://www.facebook.com",
  "username": "joao.silva.novo",
  "password": "novasenha456"
}

### 8. Deletar Credencial
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/credentials/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Deletar Conta
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/erase
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



